###---System Bindings---###
bindsym $sup+Shift+l            exec $psst "i3lock -i ~/Pictures/lock.png"

bindsym $sup+Shift+c            reload

bindsym $sup+Shift+r            restart

bindsym $sup+Shift+e            exit